{"tid":780259,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國既寶馬特別易起火?","createTime":"2018-08-15T04:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T23:12:19.000Z","uid":123177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"657fb8e05bc1629eab1822bea03137b9fd4c4baa","tid":780259,"uid":123177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:45:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1750635/org/dafb7e77070b6e2eb4cdc115ed10174c.jpg/lr-Uda2n_ZeIDokst6ImVxuoABTFVK7F-KxzLPiscyw?v=w1280r16_9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1750635%2Forg%2Fdafb7e77070b6e2eb4cdc115ed10174c.jpg%2Flr-Uda2n_ZeIDokst6ImVxuoABTFVK7F-KxzLPiscyw%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&d=Dfr5vMQy2Fz3sieZCL%2FyEjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=a493b1ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1750635/org/dafb7e77070b6e2eb4cdc115ed10174c.jpg/lr-Uda2n_ZeIDokst6ImVxuoABTFVK7F-KxzLPiscyw?v=w1280r16_9</a><br />\n<br />\n德國汽車生產商寶馬（BMW）陷於公關災難。韓國政府宣布有2.7萬輛車在未經檢驗的情況下，不准駛上馬路。該國媒體報道2018年來已39輛寶馬汽車起火，被指因排氣系統有問題。所幸沒有人在任何事件中受傷或死亡。<br />\n<br />\n寶馬已在7月召回逾2.7萬輛車，並接受緊急檢查。韓國政府稱截至周一（8月13日），逾2.7萬輛車仍未接受檢查。根據政府規定，所有收到驗車通知的車主，其座駕須通過查驗，才能開上馬路。<br />\n<br />\n韓國交通部長金賢美（Kim Hyun-mee）稱該國民眾對此非常關注。她下令地方政府禁止人們將有起火隱患而未受查的寶馬汽車駛上路面。政府已就此事展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/222845/%E5%AF%B6%E9%A6%AC%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E8%B5%B7%E7%81%AB-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E9%A0%92-%E7%A6%81%E9%A7%9B%E4%BB%A4-2-7%E8%90%AC%E8%BC%9B%E6%9C%AA%E7%B6%93%E6%AA%A2%E9%A9%97%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8A%E8%B7%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25AA%25AA%2F222845%2F%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%2593%258E%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%2581%25AB-%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25A0%2592-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%25A7%259B%25E4%25BB%25A4-2-7%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25BC%259B%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E9%25A9%2597%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BE%2597%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25B7%25AF&d=Dfr5vMQy2Fz3sieZCL%2FyEjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=8ffd7fdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/222845/%E5%AF%B6%E9%A6%AC%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E8%B5%B7%E7%81%AB-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E9%A0%92-%E7%A6%81%E9%A7%9B%E4%BB%A4-2-7%E8%90%AC%E8%BC%9B%E6%9C%AA%E7%B6%93%E6%AA%A2%E9%A9%97%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8A%E8%B7%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">點解香港/ 大陸 天氣仲熱 好似冇聽講有問題? 仲勁多人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong>"},{"pid":"e617cf4a6486b9ae173ababd648d366b6ded12e4","tid":780259,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:09:46.000Z","msg":"香港老賓著火多D"},{"pid":"d4d7575a3660597f25c87bdf630df4260d3ed7e6","tid":780259,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:59:05.000Z","msg":"01編輯係咪諗唔到點寫<br />\n呢壇野又關公關災難咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒到咁公關再勁都無用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed5f04a931ec731db0a813a0bc09b38798858ee","tid":780259,"uid":27505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:34:31.000Z","msg":"寶馬比大陸車日本車仲廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a005d600deebe83f5a3462715700a2aa2fe47c3d","tid":780259,"uid":7758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:57:25.000Z","msg":"咩年份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcebeae817456b5b22a2e7007964ea5b9b67af5","tid":780259,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T07:08:56.000Z","msg":"大陸廠既寶馬？"},{"pid":"312e81efaca0a8001bb3c801e153efe991556ef3","tid":780259,"uid":195215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":